text: Mavournee Hazel (born 20 March 1996) is an Australian actress and model. She began her acting career having many television roles, including Sam Fox: Extreme Adventures and Catching Milat. Hazel became popular for her role as Piper Willis in Neighbours. She later had roles in Halifax: Retribution, Shantaram and NCIS: Sydney.
